result.content:
You are all invited to participate in the open version of the ICPC NWERC regional, taking place this weekend in Bath, United Kingdom.

The contest is 5 hours long and starts on Sunday, 20 November 2016 at 11:00 UTC. After the online contest, solution sketches will be available here along with example code and full test data.

The contest is held on Kattis online judge. The problems and final standings will be added to Codeforces::Gym.
